{"type": "article", "id": 29969, "title": "多功能沙发", "description": "", "date": "2016-07-21T23:01:39Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 49, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160721234842gLvb2o0pWnOsCjtk.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>对于经常搬家或者是在两地奔波的人来说，拥有一件可以应对不同需求的家具就显得非常重要了。<a href=\"http://www.dearhuman.ca/projects-2/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Dear Human</a> 工作室推出的这款多功能沙发 <a href=\"http://www.dearhuman.ca/projects/sweet-seat/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sweet Seat</a> 就是设计师们根据个人经验而设计的，外形简单却不失功能性。它由五个大小不一的坐垫组成，通过橡皮圈固定在一起，看起来像是放大的礼物盒。只需要将坐垫拆开后重新排布，沙发就能转变为一张舒适的床铺。Sweet Seat 的配色走的是低调温和的风格，适用于各种室内环境，不会带来突兀的感觉。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607212356406jOCqpMD5KzidS3h.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.658333\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721235640tsk6chXz3epEx2Nw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.683333\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721235640Jr1lZXVxm9jn0Ovt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160721235641sNQloiSU0KD5cPG3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}